name: JDB
description: JDB (Just Data from Blockchain) is a powerful platform that provides live and retrospective data tracking and analysis for the Binance Smart Chain and other relevant EVM chains. With JDB, users can gain unparalleled transparency and analysis capabilities, including tracking the quality of holders, the most profitable wallets, and more. JDB also offers a range of features such as complete security checks, graphical representation of data, and automated copy trading. With JDB, users can make more informed investment decisions and maximize their profits.
